			<td class=3D"o dataAreaTop vCC" style=3D"text-align: right;">MSR/MSE</td=
>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<th class=3D"rowLabels hCR role3" scope=3D"row" style=3D"text-align: lef=
t;">Error</th>
			<td class=3D"e dataAreaLeft hCR vCC" style=3D"text-align: right;">SSE</t=
d>
			<td class=3D"e hCR vCC" style=3D"text-align: right;">df<sub>e</sub></td>
			<td class=3D"e hCR vCC" style=3D"text-align: right;">MSE</td>
			<td class=3D"e hCR vCC" style=3D"text-align: right;">&nbsp;</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<th class=3D"rowLabels hCR role3" scope=3D"row" style=3D"text-align: lef=
t;">Total</th>
			<td class=3D"o dataAreaLeft hCR vCC" style=3D"text-align: right;">SST</t=
d>
			<td class=3D"o hCR vCC" style=3D"text-align: right;">df<sub>T</sub></td>
			<td class=3D"o hCR vCC" style=3D"text-align: right;">&nbsp;</td>
			<td class=3D"o hCR vCC" style=3D"text-align: right;">&nbsp;</td>
		</tr>
	</tbody>
</table>

<p>where</p>

<p style=3D"margin-left: 40px;">SSR =3D the regression sum of squares</p>

<p style=3D"margin-left: 40px;">SSE =3D the error sum of squares</p>

<p style=3D"margin-left: 40px;">SST =3D the total sum of squares (SST =3D S=
SR + SSE)</p>

<p style=3D"margin-left: 40px;">df<sub>r</sub> =3D the model degrees of fre=
edom (equal to df<sub>r</sub> =3D <em>k</em> - 1)</p>

<p style=3D"margin-left: 40px;">df<sub>e</sub> =3D the error degrees of fre=
edom (equal to df<sub>e</sub> =3D <em>n</em> - <em>k</em>)</p>

<p style=3D"margin-left: 80px;"><em>k</em> =3D the total number of groups (=
levels of the independent variable)</p>

<p style=3D"margin-left: 80px;"><em>n</em> =3D the total number of valid ob=
servations</p>

<p style=3D"margin-left: 40px;">df<sub>T</sub> =3D the total degrees of fre=
edom (equal to<sub> </sub>df<sub>T</sub> =3D&nbsp;df<sub>r</sub> + df<sub>e=
</sub> =3D <em>n</em> - 1)</p>

<p style=3D"margin-left: 40px;">MSR =3D SSR/df<sub>r</sub> =3D the regressi=
on mean square</p>

<p style=3D"margin-left: 40px;">MSE =3D SSE/df<sub>e</sub> =3D the mean squ=
are error</p>

